- [ ] Business rules implemented explicitly as methods on the aggregate root.
- [ ] Every method signature begins with `ctx context.Context`.
- [ ] Every error is wrapped using `fmt.Errorf("...: %w", err)`.
- [ ] Application flow relies entirely on standard return patterns.
- [ ] Time retrieved exclusively via injected `Clock` interface.
- [ ] Tests synchronised using channels or wait groups.
